<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">
<head>
    <%- include('../fragmente/head') %>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="watermark">
        <b>Enache<br>Paul</b>
    </div>

    <%- include('../fragmente/header') %>

    <main>
        <section id="about-us">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <section>
                <h3>Our Story</h3>
                <p>Learn about our journey and how we started.</p>
                <blockquote>
                    <p>"Our coffee shop started with a dream to bring the best coffee experience to our community."</p>
                </blockquote>
                <figure>
                    <picture>
                        <source media="(max-width: 600px)" srcset="/resurse/ImaginiGenerale/ImagineTask1Telefon.jpg">
                        <source media="(max-width: 1200px)" srcset="/resurse/ImaginiGenerale/ImagineTask1Tableta.jpg">
                        <img src="/resurse/ImaginiGenerale/ImagineTask1Origial.webp" alt="A cup of coffee">
                    </picture>
                    <figcaption>And this is what our shoop looks like.</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </section>
            <section>
                <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                <p>Discover our mission and values.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Quality Ingredients</li>
                    <li>Exceptional Service</li>
                    <li>Community Focus</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTIUNE VIDEO NOUA -->
        <section id="video-intro">
            <h2>Demonstrație Video</h2>
            <p>Urmăriți cum se prepară o cafea perfectă în cafeneaua noastră.</p>
            
            <!-- Container adaugat pentru a controla dimensiunea -->
            <div id="video-container">
                <video controls preload="metadata" poster="/resurse/video/poster_cafea.jpg">
                    <source src="/resurse/video/cafea.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                    <source src="/resurse/video/cafea.webm" type="video/webm">
                    <track src="/resurse/subtitrari/subtitrare_ro.vtt" kind="captions" srclang="ro" label="Română" default>
                    <track src="/resurse/subtitrari/subtitrare_en.vtt" kind="captions" srclang="en" label="English">
                    Browserul dumneavoastră nu suportă tag-ul video.
                </video>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="table">
            <h2>Menu</h2>
            <div class="table-container">
                <table>
                    <caption>Our Menu</caption>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Product</th>
                            <th>Price</th>
                            <th>Description</th>
                            <th>Availability</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Coffee</td>
                            <td>$2.50</td>
                            <td>Freshly brewed coffee</td>
                            <td>In Stock</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Tea</td>
                            <td>$2.00</td>
                            <td>Selection of herbal teas</td>
                            <td>In Stock</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Cake</td>
                            <td>$3.00</td>
                            <td>Delicious chocolate cake</td>
                            <td>Limited</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Sandwich</td>
                            <td>$5.00</td>
                            <td>Freshly made sandwich</td>
                            <td>In Stock</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                    <tfoot>
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="4">Prices may vary</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tfoot>
                </table>
            </div>
            <article>
                <h3>Drinks</h3>
                <p>Explore our wide range of drinks.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Coffee</li>
                    <li>Tea</li>
                    <li>Juices</li>
                </ul>
            </article>
        </section>

        <section id="events">
            <h2>Events</h2>
            <!-- Content for Events section -->
        </section>

        <section id="announcements">
            <h2>Announcements</h2>
            <p><b>Coffee</b> is one of the most popular beverages in the world. It is made from roasted coffee beans, which are the seeds of berries from the <i>Coffea</i> plant. The two most common types of coffee beans are <b>Arabica</b> and <b>Robusta</b>.</p>
            <p>The process of making coffee involves several steps, including <dfn>grinding</dfn> the beans, brewing, and serving. The <abbr title="International Coffee Organization">ICO</abbr> oversees the global coffee trade and ensures quality standards are met.</p>
            <p><strong>Warning:</strong> Consuming too much coffee can lead to health issues such as insomnia and increased heart rate. It is recommended to limit your intake to a moderate amount.</p>
        </section>
        
        <section id="userAndStatistics">
            <h2>User and Statistics</h2>
            <p>IP-ul dumneavoastră este: <%= ip %></p>
        </section>
        
    </main>
    
    <%- include('../fragmente/footer') %>
</body>
</html>

